\">Find your course →</a></div><div class=\"border rounded-lg p-8\" style=\"border-color:var(--color-cream-darkest);background:white\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700)\">For golfers</p><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-3\">See something wrong?</h3><p class=\"mb-4 text-[15px]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink-muted)\">Phone changed, scorecard wrong, course renamed — every page has an edit button. Submit a correction and our verifier cross-checks against multiple sources.</p><a class=\"text-sm font-semibold\" style=\"color:var(--color-evergreen-950)\" href=\"/search\">Find a course to correct →</a></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t mt-20 px-6 py-12\" style=\"border-color:var(--color-cream-darkest);color:var(--color-ink-muted)\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-sm mb-8\"><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">OpenGolfAPI</h4><p class=\"mb-2\">An open almanac of American golf.</p><span class=\"inline-block text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold tracking-wider\" style=\"background:var(--color-cream-darker);color:var(--color-ink)\">ODbL 1.0</span></div><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Browse</h4><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/\">All courses</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/search\">Search</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/near-me\">Near me</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/submit\">Submit a course</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/my-edits\">My contributions</a></div><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Build</h4><a hre